WEBVTT

00:00:01.040 --> 00:00:03.360
You see it all around us.


00:00:03.360 --> 00:00:05.400
This rule of three.


00:00:05.400 --> 00:00:07.920
In the images we make,


00:00:07.920 --> 00:00:10.440
in the numbers we follow,


00:00:10.440 --> 00:00:13.440
in the make-up of every story we tell.


00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:16.800
With their beginnings, middles and ends.


00:00:17.680 --> 00:00:20.680
There's power in threes.


00:00:21.040 --> 00:00:24.040
So, let us tell you a story.


00:00:25.440 --> 00:00:28.160
A story in three parts.


00:00:28.160 --> 00:00:31.160
A story about risk.


00:00:32.680 --> 00:00:35.160
Let's meet our players.


00:00:35.160 --> 00:00:37.680
All driving the risk landscape.


00:00:37.680 --> 00:00:40.680
Shaping it from one scene to the next.


00:00:42.240 --> 00:00:46.200
But when we see risk clearly,
we can navigate it confidently


00:00:46.480 --> 00:00:49.480
and take risks intelligently.


00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:53.960
Because standing still,


00:00:53.960 --> 00:00:56.160
that's not an option.


00:00:56.160 --> 00:00:59.160
We must reinvent to stay relevant.


00:00:59.320 --> 00:01:01.360
It means taking risks. Yes,


00:01:01.360 --> 00:01:03.160
but in the right way.


00:01:03.160 --> 00:01:04.920
The way that powers growth


00:01:04.920 --> 00:01:07.920
and pushes us forward.


00:01:10.040 --> 00:01:13.040
All organisations need to build resilience


00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:16.920
in our systems, processes,
infrastructure and data.


00:01:17.480 --> 00:01:20.480
So, when the unexpected happens,
we're ready.


00:01:21.320 --> 00:01:23.040
Responding to change,


00:01:23.040 --> 00:01:24.640
protecting trust,


00:01:24.640 --> 00:01:27.160
writing the story we want told.


00:01:28.840 --> 00:01:30.960
See risk clearly.


00:01:30.960 --> 00:01:33.200
Take risk intelligently.


00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:35.920
Manage risk effectively.


00:01:35.920 --> 00:01:37.760
There's power in threes.

